<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <%- include('../includes/head.ejs') %>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://unpkg.com/aos@next/dist/aos.css" />
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-color: #0d9488; /* Teal */
            --secondary-color: #0284c7; /* Sky Blue */
            --accent-color: #f97316; /* Orange */
            --light-bg: #f8fafc;
            --white-bg: #ffffff;
            --dark-text: #0f172a;
            --soft-text: #64748b;
        }

        html {
            scroll-padding-top: 80px;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--light-bg);
            color: var(--dark-text);
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        .hero-padding {
            padding-top: 40px;
        }

        .section-padding {
            padding: 100px 0;
        }
        .section-title {
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        .section-subtitle {
            color: var(--soft-text);
            max-width: 700px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
            margin-bottom: 4rem;
        }

        /* Navbar */
        nav.navbar {
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
            box-shadow: 0 2px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        /* Hero Section */
        .hero-section {
            padding: 120px 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0fdfa 0%, #ecfeff 100%);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .hero-title {
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
            color: var(--primary-color);
            line-height: 1.2;
        }
        .hero-subtitle {
            font-size: 1.15rem;
            color: var(--soft-text);
            margin: 1.5rem 0 2.5rem;
        }
        .hero-btn {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent-color), #fb923c);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            padding: 1rem 2.8rem;
            border-radius: 9999px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 18px rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.3);
        }
        .hero-btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-4px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.4);
        }
        .hero-image {
            border-radius: 1.5rem;
            box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
        }

        /* ===== SCROLLING BANNER ===== */
        .scrolling-banner {
        position: relative;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        overflow: hidden;
        white-space: nowrap;
        padding: 0; /* Hapus padding biar mepet */
        }

        .scrolling-banner-inner {
        display: flex;
        width: max-content;
        animation: scroll-loop 25s linear infinite;
        }

        .scrolling-content {
        display: flex;
        }

        .scrolling-banner img {
        height: 60px;
        width: auto;
        flex-shrink: 0;
        margin: 0; /* Hapus jarak antar gambar */
        padding: 0;
        display: block;
        }

        /* Animasi mulus tanpa gap */
        @keyframes scroll-loop {
        from {
            transform: translateX(0);
        }
        to {
            transform: translateX(-50%);
        }
        }


        /* Features Section */
        .feature-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }
        .feature-icon {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            margin-right: 1.5rem;
            background-color: #ecfdf5;
            border-radius: 50%;
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        .feature-item h5 { font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
        .feature-item p { color: var(--soft-text); font-size: 0.95rem; }
        
        /* Systems Section (NOW DARK) */
        .systems-section {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--primary-color), var(--secondary-color));
            color: white;
        }
        .systems-section .section-title, .systems-section .section-subtitle {
            color: white;
        }
        .system-card {
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-radius: 1rem;
            padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            height: 100%;
        }
        .system-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        }
        .system-card img { height: 100px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
        .system-card h4 { color: white; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
        .system-card p { color: #d1fae5; }

        /* How It Works Section (NOW LIGHT) */
        .how-section {
            background-color: var(--white-bg);
        }
        .how-step { text-align: center; padding: 1rem; }
        .how-step .step-icon {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            background-color: #f0fdfa;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        .how-step:hover .step-icon {
            background-color: #ccfbf1;
            transform: scale(1.1);
        }
        .how-step h4 { font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; color: var(--dark-text); }
        .how-step p { color: var(--soft-text); font-size: 0.95rem; }
        
        /* Footer */
        .footer { background: var(--dark-text); color: #cbd5e1; padding: 4rem 0 2rem; }
        .footer h5 { color: white; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
        .footer a { color: var(--soft-text); text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.2s ease; }
        .footer a:hover { color: var(--accent-color); }
        .footer .copyright { border-top: 1px solid #334155; padding-top: 1.5rem; margin-top: 2rem; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--soft-text); }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('../includes/tbcare/navbar-landing.ejs') %>

    <!-- HERO SECTION -->
    <section class="hero-section" id="home">
        <div class="container hero-padding">
            <div class="row align-items-center justify-content-between" data-aos="fade-up">
                <div class="col-lg-6 text-center text-lg-left">
                    <h1 class="hero-title">Intelligent Cough Analysis for Early Tuberculosis Detection</h1>
                    <p class="hero-subtitle">
                        Our AI-powered system detects potential Tuberculosis from the sound of a cough, empowering patients and clinicians with faster, more accurate diagnostics.
                    </p>
                    <a href="/tbcare/login" class="btn hero-btn">Access Clinical Dashboard</a>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-5 d-none d-lg-block text-center mt-5 mt-lg-0">
                    <img src="/images/tbcare_landing/lungs.jpg" alt="Doctor analyzing lung scan with AI" class="img-fluid hero-image">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <div class="scrolling-banner">
        <div class="scrolling-banner-inner">
            <div class="scrolling-content">
            <img src="/images/tbcare_landing/banner.png" alt="Banner">
            <img src="/images/tbcare_landing/banner.png" alt="Banner">
            <img src="/images/tbcare_landing/banner.png" alt="Banner">
            <img src="/images/tbcare_landing/banner.png" alt="Banner">
            </div>
            <div class="scrolling-content">
            <img src="/images/tbcare_landing/banner.png" alt="Banner">
            <img src="/images/tbcare_landing/banner.png" alt="Banner">
            <img src="/images/tbcare_landing/banner.png" alt="Banner">
            <img src="/images/tbcare_landing/banner.png" alt="Banner">
            </div>
        </div>
        </div>

    
    <!-- FEATURES (WHY TBCare) SECTION -->
    <section class="section-padding" id="features">
        <div class="container">
             <div class="row align-items-center">
                <div class="col-lg-6" data-aos="fade-right">
                    <h2 class="section-title">Why Choose TBCare?</h2>
                    <p class="section-subtitle text-left ml-0 mb-5">Our platform is built on three core principles: accuracy, accessibility, and actionable insights for better patient outcomes.</p>
                    <div class="feature-item">
                        <div class="feature-icon"><i class="ri-flashlight-line"></i></div>
                        <div>
                            <h5>Early & Rapid Detection</h5>
                            <p>Identify potential risks sooner through accessible, non-invasive acoustic screening.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-item">
                        <div class="feature-icon"><i class="ri-lightbulb-line"></i></div>
                        <div>
                            <h5>Non-Invasive & Safe</h5>
                            <p>A simple cough recording is all that's needed, reducing patient discomfort and risk.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                     <div class="feature-item">
                        <div class="feature-icon"><i class="ri-bar-chart-2-line"></i></div>
                        <div>
                            <h5>Data-Driven Clinical Support</h5>
                            <p>Provide clinicians with objective data to support their diagnostic decisions and workflow.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-6 d-none d-lg-block" data-aos="fade-left" data-aos-delay="200">
                    <img src="/images/tbcare_landing/clinical.jpg" alt="Clinical Illustration" class="img-fluid rounded-lg">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SYSTEMS SECTION (NOW DARK) -->
    <section class="section-padding systems-section" id="systems">
        <div class="container text-center">
            <h2 class="section-title">An Integrated Digital Health Ecosystem</h2>
            <p class="section-subtitle" style="color: #a7f3d0;">
                From data acquisition to clinical analysis, our platform provides a seamless workflow for healthcare professionals and patients.
            </p>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-4 mb-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="0">
                    <div class="system-card">
                        <img src="/images/tbcare_landing/device/Hardware.png" alt="Precision Recording Device">
                        <h4>Precision Recording Device</h4>
                        <p>High-fidelity sensors capture nuanced audio data for accurate cough analysis.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4 mb-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
                    <div class="system-card">
                        <img src="/images/tbcare_landing/device/Web.png" alt="Clinical Analytics Dashboard">
                        <h4>Clinical Analytics Dashboard</h4>
                        <p>A secure web platform for clinicians to review patient data and AI-generated insights.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4 mb-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
                    <div class="system-card">
                        <img src="/images/tbcare_landing/device/mobile.png" alt="Patient & Provider Mobile App">
                        <h4>Patient & Provider App</h4>
                        <p>Empowers patients to perform self-screening and manage their health records.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- HOW IT WORKS SECTION (NOW LIGHT) -->
    <section class="section-padding how-section" id="process">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row text-center" data-aos="fade-in">
                <div class="col">
                    <h2 class="section-title">End-to-End Diagnostic Workflow</h2>
                    <p class="section-subtitle">A simple and connected process from patient to physician.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row text-center">
                <div class="col-md-3 how-step" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="0">
                    <div class="step-icon"><img src="https://img.icons8.com/ios/50/0d9488/microphone--v1.png" alt="Record Icon" height="40"></div>
                    <h4>1. Record Cough</h4>
                    <p>The patient records a cough sample using the TBCare hardware.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-3 how-step" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
                    <div class="step-icon"><img src="https://img.icons8.com/ios/50/0d9488/cloud-sync.png" alt="Server Icon" height="40"></div>
                    <h4>2. AI Server Analysis</h4>
                    <p>The recording is securely sent to our server and analyzed by the AI to determine TB suspicion.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-3 how-step" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
                    <div class="step-icon"><img src="https://img.icons8.com/ios/50/0d9488/medical-doctor.png" alt="Doctor Icon" height="40"></div>
                    <h4>3. Review on Web Dashboard</h4>
                    <p>Clinicians receive and review the preliminary results (TB/Non-TB) on their dashboard.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-3 how-step" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
                    <div class="step-icon"><img src="https://img.icons8.com/ios/50/0d9488/appointment-reminders--v1.png" alt="Notification Icon" height="40"></div>
                    <h4>4. Patient Notification</h4>
                    <p>Results are sent to the patient's mobile app. A notification is sent if a follow-up is required.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <%- include('../includes/tbcare/footer-landing.ejs') %>
    <%- include('../includes/end.ejs') %>
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/aos@next/dist/aos.js"></script>
    <script>
      AOS.init({
          duration: 700,
          once: true
      });
    </script>
</body>
</html>